<!doctype html>
<html>
  <link rel="stylesheet" href = "../css/style.css">
  <head>
    <title>Dragon!</title>
  </head>
  <body><div class = "health-gold">
      <ul class = "health">
        <% for i in 0..@user_dragon.health do %>
        <li> <img align = "center" class = "heart" src = "http://bit.ly/1EXiIKQ"> </li>
        <% end %>
      </ul>
      <p class = "story-paragraph" style = "text-align: right">
        <%= @user_dragon.gold %>
        <img align = "right" style = "width: 3vw; margin-right: 11%;" src = "http://bit.ly/1EkWS9u">
      </p>
    </div>
    <img class = "background-dragon centered" style = "opacity: 0.15" src = "../images/background-dragon.png">
    <img class="centered img_small" style = "top: 10%;" src="../images/Title.png">
    <center><p class="centered story-paragraph" style = "top: 35%;"><b>You are able to make it inside. You venture to his vault and steal 600 gold! As you are escaping you are confronted by the wizard. He summons a beam of light that strikes you and does 6 damage. You make it out with your life and a good sum of gold. You go back to your lair and bathe in your wealth. THE END
</b></p>
     </center>
    <img class="centered img_small" style = "top: 60%;" src="../images/Mage.png">
   <form method = "POST" action = "page1">
      <input name = "name" class = "hidden-input" type = "hidden" value = '<%= @user_dragon.name %>'>
      <input name = "sex" class = "hidden-input" type = "hidden" value = '<%= @user_dragon.sex %>'>
     <input name = "color" class = "hidden-input" type = "hidden" value = '<%= @user_dragon.color %>'>
      <input name = "skin_type" class = "hidden-input" type = "hidden" value = '<%= @user_dragon.skin_type %>'>
      <input name = "health" class = "hidden-input" type = "hidden" value = '<%= @user_dragon.health %>'>
      <input name = "gold" class = "hidden-input" type = "hidden" value = '<%= @user_dragon.gold %>'>
      <input class = "centered" type="submit" style = "top: 80%; left: 30%;" value="Play Again?">
    </form>
    <form method = "POST" action = "../create_character">
      <input name = "name" class = "hidden-input" type = "hidden" value = '<%= @user_dragon.name %>'>
      <input name = "sex" class = "hidden-input" type = "hidden" value = '<%= @user_dragon.sex %>'>
      <input name = "color" class = "hidden-input" type = "hidden" value = '<%= @user_dragon.color %>'>
      <input name = "skin_type" class = "hidden-input" type = "hidden" value = '<%= @user_dragon.skin_type %>'>
      <input name = "health" class = "hidden-input" type = "hidden" value = '<%= @user_dragon.health %>'>
      <input name = "gold" class = "hidden-input" type = "hidden" value = '<%= @user_dragon.gold %>'>
      <input class = "centered" type="submit" style = "top: 80%; left: 70%;" value="Create New Dragon?">
    </form>
  </body>
</html>
